query:
INSERT INTO merchants (userId, merchantNumber, businessName, businessType, location, cnpsStatus, cmuStatus, isVerified, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT id, CONCAT('MRC-ADMIN-', LPAD(id, 5, '0')), CONCAT(name, ' - Commerce'), 'Commerce général', 'Abidjan, Côte d''Ivoire', 'active', 'active', 1, NOW(), NOW() 
FROM users 
WHERE name LIKE '%PATRICK%' OR name LIKE '%SOMET%' 
LIMIT 1;
